Package com.weebly.opus1269.clipman.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlarmReceiver
    BroadcastReceiver that cleans up old entries in the database
    AutoStartReceiver
    This BroadcastReceiver starts the ClipboardWatcherService at boot time and adds a daily alarm to clean-up the database
    ClipboardWatcherService
    An app private Service to listen for changes to the clipboard, persist them to storage using ClipContentProvider and push them to registered fcm devices
    MyFcmListenerService
    A service that listens for messages from firebase
    MyInstanceIDListenerService
    This FirebaseInstanceIdService listens for changes to the regToken
    MyWidgetProvider
    Manage our app's widget
    PackageReplacedReceiver  
    RefreshTokenJobService
    JobService to handle FirebaseInstanceIdService refreshToken()
